gray.description: Define if image is gray scale. Default `false`

rounded.description: Show buttons rounded or square. Default `true`

type.description: Type of button. Default `"email"`, possibles values are: `facebook`, `google`, `linkedin`, `twitter`, `telegram`, `whatsapp`, `pinterest`, `vk`, `ok`, `reddit`, `tumblr`, `livejournal`, `email`, `viber`

directLink.description: Indicates if it is redirected to a link within the social network or a floating window is displayed to share the link using the social network. Default `true`
